<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Interview Invitation - {{recruiterCompany}}</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #FAFAFA; color: #222222;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style="background-color: #28a745; padding: 24px; color: #ffffff;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">
                Interview Invitation from {{recruiterCompany}}</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; background-color: #ffffff;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Dear {{candidateName}},</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">We are pleased to inform you that we would like to invite you for an interview for the position of <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> at {{recruiterCompany}}.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Here are the details of the interview:</p>
            
            <h2 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;">Position: {{jobTitle}}</h2>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Date: {{interviewDate}}</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Time: {{interviewTime}}</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Location: {{interviewLocation}}</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Please reply to this email to confirm your availability for the interview. If you have any questions or require further information, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:{{recruiterEmail}}" style="color: #000; text-decoration:none;">{{recruiterEmail}}</a>.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">We look forward to meeting you and discussing the opportunity in more detail.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 24px;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                For more information, please visit our website or contact us at <a href="mailto:{{recruiterEmail}}" target="_blank" style="color: #000; text-decoration:none;">{{recruiterEmail}}</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
